1. d4 e5 2. dxe5 d6 3. exd6 Bxd6 4. Nf3 Nc6 5. Nc3 Bg4 6. h3 Bf5 { Bh5 was fine too. } 7. g4 Bg6 8. h4 h6 { h5 was good too } 9. b3 { There is a clear best move here that wasn't played. } 9... Qd7 { To avoid Nd5. But in fact we would simply have played Qe6. } 10. Bh3 Nge7 { Long castle was actually the best move! } 11. g5 Bf5 12. Bxf5 Nxf5 13. Bb2 O-O-O 14. e4 Rhe8 15. O-O { Pause. } 15... Nfe7 { The best move was Nxh4 } 16. e5 Qg4+ 17. Kh2 Bxe5+ 18. Nxe5 { Taking with the bishop was actually better, can you see why? } 18... Qxh4+ 19. Kg2 Rxd1 20. Raxd1 Nxe5 21. Ne2 Qxg5+ 22. Ng3 *


